title: Olympic Channel podcast with Jamie Anderson and Eve Muirhead
description: Grab your backstage pass to PyeongChang 2018 for the first episode of the Olympic Channel podcast. We learn the Korean word for 'awesome'. Plus, we sit down with Olympic gold medallist snowboarder Jamie Anderson and Olympic bronze medallist curler Eve Muirhead.
